text: Freudenstadt is a rural district (Landkreis) in the middle of Baden- Württemberg, Germany. Neighboring districts are Rastatt, Calw, Tübingen, Zollernalbkreis, Rottweil and the Ortenaukreis. The capital is Freudenstadt. The district is in the middle part of the Black Forest mountains.
